《'''口吃男恋语'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Stutterer'''''}}）是一部实景短剧，由[[班杰明·克利里|班杰明·克利里]]执导和编剧<ref>{{Cite web|title = North Yorkshire movie Stutterer lands Oscar chance|url = http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/entertainment/14247543.North_Yorkshire_movie_Stutterer_lands_Oscar_chance/|website = The Northern Echo|access-date = 2016-02-03|archive-date = 2016-02-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160225135903/http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/entertainment/14247543.North_Yorkshire_movie_Stutterer_lands_Oscar_chance/|dead-url = no}}</ref>，并由[[塞雷娜·阿米蒂奇|塞雷娜·阿米蒂奇]]和[[珊·克里斯多福·奧格爾維|珊·克里斯多福·奧格爾維]]监制<ref>{{Cite web|title = Serena Armitage & Shan Christopher Ogilvie Discuss Stutterer|url = http://www.femalefirst.co.uk/movies/serena-armitage-and-shan-christopher-ogilvie-discuss-stutterer-908627.html|website = www.femalefirst.co.uk|access-date = 2016-02-04|archive-date = 2016-02-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204173927/http://www.femalefirst.co.uk/movies/serena-armitage-and-shan-christopher-ogilvie-discuss-stutterer-908627.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==剧情==
格林伍德，一个孤单的排版师为了一段浪漫的关系而努力去克服他的说话障碍。

